metadata.name: Golden Breeze
metadata.description:
The golden and shiny breeze. 
Rare and momentary.
Unique and special.
It passes through our lives only a few times.
At the slightest glimpse of it
we must grab it, squeeze it,
dive deep and let it take over.
Our duty as intelligent beings is to enjoy, 
to delight to the maximum of every second of happiness
and make it worthwhile. 
Because once this moment is over
it will never return. 
It will fade away forever
and until a new one arises we wait.
